{"tid":123604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"燒山預測林鄭蠃面為 99.99%","createTime":"2017-02-17T03:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T05:05:43.000Z","uid":20563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"817ec757cca97253b96d09861ca4f15268cab397","tid":123604,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"贏面99.99% 網民歡呼：香港有救<br />\n<br />\n2017-02-17 00:01:14 HKT<br />\n<br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n特首提名期在2月14日展開，時事評論員蕭若元（蕭生）昨日在其Youtube頻道「蕭若元：最新蕭析」欄目，上載題目為「林鄭取壓倒性提名票 轉軚機會甚微」片段，預測林鄭月娥手握680、690至710、720提名票，並提到他曾指林鄭勝出的機率是99.99%，四捨五入即幾近百分百。不過，蕭生亦有「燈神」稱號，言論一出即有網民留言「香港有救」，「好希望你今次做燈神﻿」、「蕭生你要繼續燈呀，鬍鬚先有機會，加油！」<br />\n<br />\n片段中蕭生表示，根據多份報章報道，林鄭現時已掌握近400提名票，提到《HK01》估計是400票，《NOW政情》則估計她「坐六望七」，而他估計是多於600票，「我相信一定600票以上」，而選委會分批交上提名。他又指，即使民建聯聲稱「唔綑綁」，但據聞中聯辦會將已填好的提名表逐一要求民建聯選委簽署，相信沒有人膽敢不簽；他預計曾俊華能取得的建制派提名票，不會在50票以上。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，「葉劉入閘係好重要」，因為只有葉劉淑儀可以令林鄭在第一輪投票中未過半數而未能當選，能證明林鄭得不到建制的整體支持，亦能令林鄭和葉劉互相攻擊，即使第二輪投票林鄭當選，亦會增加其管治成本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170217&amp;guid=56313823&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170217%26guid%3D56313823%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4c0ce764\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170217%26guid%3D56313823%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=3e2c72bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170217&amp;guid=56313823&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"226d1d8b7c80268ddeda1ca2dbbeded9b17a8a25","tid":123604,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EBgk0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EBgk0.jpg&h=22e67536&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fa2b7d0e7828a802b48d8f61d33c4f75ab020dc","tid":123604,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F24ziq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F24ziq.jpg&h=8e91b864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蠃硬，燒山話既"},{"pid":"43cf481a37802381c4f9fb97648bd66d405663d9","tid":123604,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"多謝蕭生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb73eac20c6368c02080faf8798ca55e28fb5bd","tid":123604,"uid":22574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"順便燈埋胡官同長毛冇得做ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee139b8d691948bcc3c53f885acd0e0ae862963","tid":123604,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順便燈埋胡官同長毛冇得做ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一句，薯片做唔到未得囉"},{"pid":"b996a7fef40bb641ddfb4b65a7fde5735a69ff41","tid":123604,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"燒山好嘢 多謝燒山 支持燒山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1385a0cad1fe0806eec6c1ccc14aaa463887826f","tid":123604,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"多謝燒生"},{"pid":"8d0dc52e918b0280b7412d7cba0b61ca7864e511","tid":123604,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:41:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">燒山大法好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">林鄭一定輸</s